{"tid":442363,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"［尋公仔］巴打絲打求救 揾唔番買呢隻野果間鋪","createTime":"2017-10-20T14:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T14:26:48.000Z","uid":33391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f60a8b518a00813022104250c3a2fd056779cb84","tid":442363,"uid":33391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/20/222127_1e28b08dde8f0f4f9ea73e16f51466b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2F222127_1e28b08dde8f0f4f9ea73e16f51466b7.jpg&h=51362537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻熊仔係我大約03年果陣喺奧海城嘅一間鋪頭買 果陣超鐘意佢 日日攬住佢瞓 點知有一次帶佢去旅行走果陣就唔見左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大海撈針 如果有巴絲打知道邊到可以揾番佢嘅就話比我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都知張相好矇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻熊仔身係白色，着住一件連帽嘅灰白間條hoodies㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求大神相助"}]}